Class energy

  • java.lang.Object
    • Core.energy

  • public class energy
extends java.lang.Object
    ML.Player - Energy Controller

    - This class manages the audio output

    - This class works as controller of ePlayer class

    - Singleton class and its object is never passed outside

    Version:
    0.2c

    Class-wise Change Log: 0.1c -> 0.2c

    - Added formal documentation

    - Tweaked finalise() method

    Author:
    msahil432
